\[\mbox{Var}(\rho^{\prime}BY) = \mbox{Var}[\rho^{\prime}(B-A)Y+\rho^{\prime}AY]\] \[= \mbox{Var}[\rho^{\prime}(B-A)Y]+\mbox{Var}(\rho^{\prime}AY)+2 \mbox{Cov}[\rho^{\prime}(B-A)Y,\rho^{\prime}AY].\]

