\[\begin{bmatrix}\mu_{1}\\ \mu_{1}\\ \mu_{2}\end{bmatrix}=X\beta=AY=\begin{bmatrix}y_{2}\\ y_{2}\\ y_{3}\end{bmatrix}.\]

